I think the issue is the registry image has a volume defined, /var/lib/registry.
```
          "Image": "sha256:bc0d86131a2db92f18b8413a38da41718748b152024be47a8bc9413fa1d50a95",
            "Volumes": {
                "/var/lib/registry": {}
            },
```  

That's not getting created as it should be.  So the stat is failing for the srcPath at: https://github.com/containers/buildah/blob/master/run.go#L513  due to it not being created.  Then the next time through the volumePath now exists so it never gets into that stat check code to fail again and then moves on to the bind mounts.  Not sure how to correct it yet, need to dig further.
